    "Title": "Moderate Repairs Needed: ~mission(Location)",
    "Description": "Hello,\n\nWe've received word that a devastating storm hit <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> which caused some damage to the structures. Our technician on site is still trying to figure out what they can fix but they can\u2019t get everything. If you bring <EM4>six fuses</EM4>, a <EM4>salvaging tool</EM4>, and <EM4>enough RMC canisters to repair around five pipes</EM4>, we should be able to handle any remaining repairs.\n\nIf you need more information on maintenance work, see <EM4>\u201cCornerstone Developments' Guide to Maintenance\u201d</EM4> entry in your mobiGlas Journal.\n\nThanks,\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
